      "comment": "ROCKET SUSIE (2) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts ago but finished fourth last time (18.29) at this track. Has ability and can bounce back. ROUGH GIRL RUBY (4) pinged the lids last start from an awkward draw and led throughout to score (17.88) at this track in a Other over 305m. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. JAZZY BOO (5) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 6th at Angle Park in TG1-4W company. Has a good record here at this journey. Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Should be about the money. LUST TO BURN (1) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
